p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng thu h\u00fat \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n s\u1eafc v\u00e0ng tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/15258\/2noi-that-phong-khach-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=484.16666666666663\" alt=\"Kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/694997373cba4d03a4bd9ab2f76a7d45\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>K\u1ec7 tivi treo t\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ecf g\u1ecdn, ch\u1eeba kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i cho \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/15269\/thiet-ke-phong-kahch-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=484.16666666666663\" alt=\"kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/8568323c626b4e1685995c44a19571f1\" \/><\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>B\u1ed9 b\u00e0n \u0103n 6 gh\u1ebf sang tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0m v\u00e1ch ng\u0103n ng\u1ea7m tinh t\u1ebf gi\u1eefa kh\u00f4ng gian kh\u00e1ch b\u1ebfp<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/15266\/khong-gian-noi-that-phong-kahch-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=525\" alt=\"ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb9p\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/f083daa1634e4a339c9caad13027d426\" \/><\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>B\u1ed1 tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00ed s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0<\/em><\/p>\n<p><strong>M\u1eabu 2: Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\u00a0kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gam m\u00e0u m\u1ea1nh k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t m\u00e0u\u00a0s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1eadp<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17439\/2-ghe-sofa-cung-ban-tra-nghe-thuat-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=524.2708333333333\" alt=\"thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u00e1t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/6bf85627d71042ed83cbfa8d579ea4e3\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sofa ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 b\u1ebfp \u0103n<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17438\/1-noi-that-phong-khach-mau-xanh-tre-trung-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=523.5416666666666\" alt=\"t\u1eeb b\u1ebfp nh\u00ecn ra ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/27d0f549d437449cb486f5c60986447c\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>T\u1eeb b\u1ebfp nh\u00ecn ra ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17427\/4-bo-ban-an-4-ghe-phong-khach-lien-bep-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=522.8125\" alt=\"ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp li\u1ec1n ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/446e90d97e4845f1b5bae408ffcc4ee1\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch li\u1ec1n b\u1ebfp c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng gian r\u1ed9ng, tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi gam m\u00e0u xanh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng, mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, b\u1eaft m\u1eaft v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, b\u00e0n \u0103n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p l\u00ed, v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<h4><span id=\"Mau_3Toi_uu_anh_sang_tu_nhien_cho_can_phong_khach_thoang_dang\"><strong>M\u1eabu 3:\u00a0T\u1ed1i \u01b0u \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng<\/strong><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/19197\/1-ghe-sofa-chu-i-sat-tuong-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=481.97916666666663\" alt=\"Gh\u1ebf sofa ch\u1eef I \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>C\u1eeda \u0111i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u00e8m 2 l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft ngu\u1ed3n s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i n\u00f3ng oi b\u1ee9c<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/19200\/1-khong-gian-khach-bep-thoang-dang-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=481.97916666666663\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e8n th\u1ea3 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Chi\u1ebfc th\u1ea3m l\u00f4ng m\u1ec1m m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ph\u00e2n chia khu v\u1ef1c ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch sang tr\u1ecdng<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/19196\/1-bo-ghe-sofa-6-ghe-em-ai-sang-trong-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=481.97916666666663\" alt=\"R\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch b\u1ebfp\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gam m\u00e0u x\u00e1m tr\u1eafng cho nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t xen l\u1eabn m\u00e0u n\u00e2u g\u1ed7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p<\/em><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 h\u00e0i h\u00f2a gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u1edbi nhau l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch. S\u1ef1 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch d\u1ea1ng m\u1edf \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i.<\/p>\n<h4 id=\"dien-tich-lon\"><span id=\"Mau_4_Phong_khachnho_lien_thong_voi_bep_an_hien_dai\"><strong>M\u1eabu 4: Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\u00a0nh\u1ecf li\u00ean th\u00f4ng v\u1edbi b\u1ebfp \u0103n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/span><\/h4>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17425\/13-vach-ngan-phong-khach-sau-ke-tivi-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=420\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/778f7a4fac384e1c8a6df49426e24f4b\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, trang tr\u00ed hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17423\/11-ke-tivi-phong-khach-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=420\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/66fbd3c8d41843a791e9f026930a5424\" \/><br \/>\n<em>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng ng\u0103n n\u1eafp v\u00e0 logic<\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec7n nghi ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho nh\u1eefng sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17412\/21-tu-ruou-trang-tri-da-nang-phong-bep-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?width=700&amp;height=420\" alt=\"N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch\" data-udi=\"umb:\/\/media\/857ed95150c144638e49ac3c2eed3e6a\" \/><\/em><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><img src=\"https:\/\/noithatmanhhe.vn\/media\/17414\/23-tu-bep-chu-i-phoi-mau-tre-trung-noi-that-manh-he.jpg?wid